trans-unit.source: Represents a subscription to a timer event.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma assinatura de um evento do temporizador.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> objects are added to the timer queue associated with a workflow instance in order to send a message to a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> at a specified time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> os objetos são adicionados à fila de timer associada a uma instância de fluxo de trabalho para enviar uma mensagem para um determinado <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> em um horário especificado.

trans-unit.source: When the time specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> is reached, the workflow runtime engine sends a message containing the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Quando o tempo especificado por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> for atingido, o fluxo de trabalho mecanismo de tempo de execução envia uma mensagem que contém o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> para o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> especificado por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The timer queue associated with a workflow instance is contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.
trans-unit.target: A fila de timer associada a uma instância de fluxo de trabalho está contida no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.

trans-unit.source: You can examine <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to determine which activities are waiting on a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>.
trans-unit.target: Você pode examinar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objetos retornados pelo <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> para determinar quais atividades estão esperando um determinado <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> both use timer event subscriptions to provide part of their functionality.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> usam assinaturas de evento de timer para fornecer a parte de sua funcionalidade.
